body:
So I recently got into getting sounds for my texture pack (since I'm bored lol) and I have a squeaky voice so my voice would not be ideal.I searched on the Internet and found amazing bow sounds,like it says rekt instead of the ding :P.I had trouble finding a good hit sound,so I went here.What in looking for is a robotic voice (male) saying eZ when I hit people.

So,without further ado,GIMME SOUNDS!
